Job Title: GenAI Data Scientist Location: Dallas, TX or New Jersey or Tampa, FLJob Summary: We are looking for a Data Scientist with a passion for Generative AI to support AI/ML model development and data-driven innovation. The role focuses on applying Python and SQL skills to prepare data, build prototypes, and contribute to AI-powered solutions.Must-Have Skills: • Proficiency in Python (Pandas, NumPy, Scikit-learn, etc.).

Strong knowledge of SQL for querying and data manipulation.
